details.name: Song of the Siren
details.description: All enemies in range of the Naga Siren are put into a magical stasis where they cannot act or be attacked. Using Song of the Siren again will end the duration early. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Song of the Siren regenerates all nearby allies for 10% of their health per second.
